using contracts-for-difference provided by CeFDex AG.  Frankfurt-based CeFDex will offer investors in Spain access
to CFDs on Spanish equities in the IBEX 35 and  20 other mid-cap
stocks , according to Harald Patt, the member of CeFDexâ€™s
management board responsible for software development,
